,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但到底佢用咩途徑去娜美星呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳩估<br />\n比達一日未出場，莊子都係同阿樂一齊<br />\n更何況 , 主角係知呢個時期 , 莊子老豆已經整到太空船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早出發搵大長老開發潛力 , 再用娜美星龍珠返地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時比達敗走 , 去到娜美星都冇龍珠用<br />\n自然菲利冇特殊原因留係娜美星 , 冇菲利炸爆無限 , 悟空就唔識變超西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b512e5342c2ba98c8fbfc7beaaf3b0c8e6662c87","tid":36753,"uid":20312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"留名追故"},{"pid":"c7b6f27997a19358db00e6effd3b240dcdd08016","tid":36753,"uid":59777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿樂挑戰無閑最強地球人稱號"},{"pid":"76390656e774e47e9519535f32f9413a73ea70f6","tid":36753,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"幾時有下集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e56d2f7193798116b65a37aab8ede24627545e3","tid":36753,"uid":31872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但到底佢用咩途徑去娜美星呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳩估<br />\n比達一日未出場，莊子都係同阿樂一齊<br />\n更何況 , 主角係知呢個時期 , 莊子老豆已經整到太空船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早出發搵大長老開發潛力 , 再用娜美星龍珠返地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時比達敗走 , 去到娜美星都冇龍珠用<br />\n自然菲利冇特殊原因留係娜美星 , 冇菲利炸爆無限 , 悟空就唔識變超西 <img src=\"/assets/