ote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/114002_f0d9a41f413c7e485bb48b537c5cfcfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F114002_f0d9a41f413c7e485bb48b537c5cfcfc.jpg&h=5bf38aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該都唔得<br />\n可能阿樂提早去執左天神隻太空船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n悟空後尾去果架太空船唔係佢老豆整？ <br />\n太耐冇睇 , 記唔到咁詳細 , 只知佢一定偷左步去娜美星搵大長老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7634dd671649e486775e58ab42dfbfc2f8618f","tid":36753,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但到底佢用咩途徑去娜美星呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳩估<br />\n比達一日未出場，莊子都係同阿樂一齊<br />\n更何況 , 主角係知呢個時期 , 莊子老豆已經整到太空船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早出發搵大長老開發潛力 , 再用娜美星龍珠返地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時比達敗走 , 去到娜美星都冇龍珠用<br />\n自然菲利冇特殊原因留係娜美星 , 冇菲利炸爆無限 , 悟空就唔識變超西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人變超西，最後俾人造人滅團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人造人係果陣好似未整到咁勁<br />\n16,17,18 號個山窿 漫畫都大約有講(前題係主角個世界觀係base on佢睇晒成套龍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"90e59fba4f353feb1d72e0dce713696ee1a2c914","tid":36753,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"阿樂 啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b5de47c53e305bf4273bd02a1ecd24a9553590","tid":36753,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"悟飯一定係啊樂個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2b03c6800e64b64d000779a107cb61bbbc1f45","tid":36753,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>悟飯一定係啊樂個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一定係求左神龍變自己做超級撒亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d4cc44cf4d9a8cb24ba202a4e2567002c25a91","tid":36753,"uid":64426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a33f60e146cda67687f8f72ef19b969a7fbdcfcf","tid":36753,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但到底佢用咩途徑去娜美星呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鳩估<br />\n比達一日未出場，莊子都係同阿樂一齊<br />\n更何況 , 主角係知呢個時期 , 莊子老豆已經整到太空船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早出發搵大長老開發潛力 , 再用娜美星龍珠返地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時比達敗走 , 去到娜美星都冇龍珠用<br />\n自然菲利冇特殊原因留係娜美星 , 冇菲利炸爆無限 , 悟空就唔識變超西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/13/114002_f0d9a41f413c7e485bb48b537c5cfcfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F13%2F114002_f0d9a41f413c7e485bb48b537c5cfcfc.jpg&h=5bf38aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該都唔得<br />\n可能阿樂提早去執左天神隻太空船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n悟空後尾去果架太空船唔係佢老豆整？ <br />\n太耐冇睇 , 記唔到咁詳細 , 只知佢一定偷左步去娜美星搵大長老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得而家已經補左少少莊子童年故事，<br />\n佢可以話搵積克黎帶佢去娜美星。"},{"pid":"906461df41107e52817aa2c899b472339790f51e","tid":36753,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockq