:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n一開波KO左個博士就唔會有人造人同CELL<br />\n唔畀人吸能量就唔會有布歐<br />\n所以最大問題應該得菲利</blockquote><br />\n主角一開頭就記得返呢次難關係培植人<br />\n佢實會記得打後<br />\n俾博士穿心<br />\n俾斯路仔打斷手<br />\n俾布歐變朱古力 呢d柒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n期待佢勁過無限悟空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過到菲利呢關再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n布歐篇阿樂夠唔夠STAGE 1菲利打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"321f0d52776a76f2f5120dc8de8712751d1d24f3","tid":36753,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n過到菲利呢關再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n布歐篇阿樂夠唔夠STAGE 1菲利打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頂盡贏到精英軍團個捷斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 菲利篇之後既阿樂唔多見有修練"},{"pid":"d5fe32a6102048c041b8b7aabec2b12b547a5821","tid":36753,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608490000e8403f03bf7d9e53448a769aa683971","tid":36753,"uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時有下一集 好想知點去娜美星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182c12a79e526e8045f8afc122f5cafd1c7b4dc9","tid":36753,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n過到菲利呢關再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n布歐篇阿樂夠唔夠STAGE 1菲利打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頂盡贏到精英軍團個捷斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 菲利篇之後既阿樂唔多見有修練</blockquote><br />\n佢俾培植人爆死左之後係界王練過下<br />\n但同期佢地成班最強係天津飯(天津飯唔係人類 , 所以我先唔講最強地球人) <br />\n布歐篇壓到瘦布歐兩野<br />\n係阿樂覺得點追都追唔到 , 先唔再練 , 廢事拖其他人後腳(斯路篇)<br />\n如果佢keep住練數據上應該抽得贏菲利1,2,3 形 ( 菲利2形 魔童都抽得贏 , 3先俾人秒  , 菲利最終係唔知幾多倍化3形 ) <br />\n要佢變身前輕敵一個龜波氣功 + 界王拳 ko佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過菲利一出最終形就算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcad189ce263e7a0a0b81c2bd68fb6893e798af3","tid":36753,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"識玩一定死一次用笑話tum佢教你界王拳同最重要既元氣彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bf916797863319f3d54f470273943c283b36f4","tid":36753,"uid":56957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9eacb503ebd8f023c198a3c2622b9748c9130802","tid":36753,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"潛解無限當年過萬戰力<br />\n應該己經立巴之上未過比達<br />\n不過佢有咁多年時間用龍珠同精神時間房<br />\n可以做好多野<br />\n悟空係咪之前仲有死，蛇道趕緊黎都未知"},{"pid":"5cf036da325cbd3863ab0493b0cec649f0197d87","tid":36753,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"依類作品多數最後都會失去莊子，好期待"},{"pid":"6a10e5e989298293d80e658ca99ffee5a27f572c","tid":36753,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d405660262f9bce5fb4865d6ea3e0226b5a8a08","tid":36753,"uid":16511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:12:50.000Z","msg":"好撚想用莊子拆野"},{"pid":"1cc8ead0e8eafdae42bf21626174bffba957d556","tid":36753,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"好撚正"},{"pid":"5b973d378800bdde5dd37271346761f8e1a3f133","tid":36753,"uid":8768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73edd70034de7699030c360eaf0a6f1c807e865","tid":36753,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:47:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潛解無限當年過萬戰力<br />\n應該己經立巴之上未過比達<br />\n不過佢有咁多年時間用龍珠同精神時間房<br />\n可以做好多野<br />\n悟空係咪之前仲有死，蛇道趕緊黎都未知</blockquote><br />\n例如將用龍珠自己變做撒亞人體質"},{"pid":"e64afc31e2cfc2034b71f8f6b478f624a6b30b77","tid":36753,"uid":31872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:11:24.000Z","msg":"我諗應該唔會大改劇情卦，大改左個故事就冇共鳴了"},{"pid":"cbfb78f2e2510b0a72dea9a9085407912b33046e","tid":36753,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T22:24:34.000Z","msg":"但係d地球人唔死 冇去界王度學野 之後斯路篇會唔會死得仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93c61bb1f05191f6e2b3aeee3c872fa10a8b223","tid":36753,"uid":1493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T22:47:16.000Z","msg":"真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3930342cce49e170a344bca7966dc6290ecb5c","tid":36753,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係d地球人唔死 冇去界王度學野 之後斯路篇會唔會死得仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n解決左目前問題<br />\n不過失去左對戰一級級勁上去的敵人<br />\n慢慢成長的機會<br />\n同埋悟空唔知去左邊<br />\n最有潛力果個又無左練級機會"},{"pid":"db500fd07c975aad7aa15a24e58b0ecb19573c24","tid":36753,"uid":20641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86c820212e6c4b992ce2c0f133a5bca7e6067d6","tid":36753,"uid":2701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"同無閑學氣圓斬直接秒左比達同菲利佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e95e2a1a26b2fa031c900908e9b72ac37af02b","tid":36753,"uid":24597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"幾時下一集"},{"pid":"62d840bf1c538be7ceff70b80bf833f28ccaad2a","tid":36753,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係d地球人唔死 冇去界王度學野 之後斯路篇會唔會死得仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n解決左目前問題<br />\n不過失去左對戰一級級勁上去的敵人<br />\n慢慢成長的機會<br />\n同埋悟空唔知去左邊<br />\n最有潛力果個又無左練級機會</blockquote><br />\n殺左博士又點會有人造人同斯路"},{"pid":"fb0c5bc2d6ef48c5b3cadbfca89089d3d24aaf89","tid":36753,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"好睇過龍珠超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9082568e49c3fd3cdd9087e23d8b121ea00dce5","tid":36753,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T21:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時下一集</blockquote><br />\n2017<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}